<h3 id="hahn" class="math">{{ section }}.2 Hahn分解</h3>
<div class="math-book">
<i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark"></i> <a href="#miyajima"><cite lang="ja">谷島</cite></a> Sec. 8.2
</div>
<p>\((\varOmega,\,\mathcal{F})\)を可測空間とする．\(\mathcal{F}\)上の集合族\((F_n)_{n \in \mathbb{Z}_+}\)で\(i \neq j\)ならば\(F_i \cap F_j = \emptyset\)を満たすようなものを任意にとる．関数\(\mu\colon \mathcal{F} \to \mathbb{R}\)が
\begin{align*}
  \mu \left(\bigcup_{n = 1}^\infty F_n \right) = \sum_{n = 1}^\infty \mu (F_n)
\end{align*}
を満たすならば，\(\mu\)を符号付き測度と呼ぶ．\(\mu(\emptyset) = \mu(\emptyset) + \mu(\emptyset)\)より\(\mu(\emptyset) = 0\)である．</p>
<p>集合\(E^+ \in \mathcal{F}\)が，\(F \subseteq E^+\)を満たす任意の\(F \in \mathcal{F}\)について\(\mu(F) \geq 0\)を満たすとき，\(E^+\)を\(\mu\)-positive集合と呼ぶ．同様に集合\(E^- \in \mathcal{F}\)が，\(F \subseteq E^-\)任意の\(F \in \mathcal{F}\)について\(\mu(F) \leq 0\)を満たすとき，\(E^-\)を\(\mu\)-negative集合と呼ぶ．</p>
<p><strong>証明</strong>
\begin{align*}
  u := \sup \{\mu(E) \mid E \in \mathcal{F},\,E\text{ \(\mu\)-positive}\}
\end{align*}
空集合は\(\mu\)-positiveだから\(u \geq 0\)である．
\begin{align*}
  E^+ = \bigcup_{n = 1}^\infty E_n,\quad E^- = X \setminus E^+
\end{align*}
</p>
