<h3 id="borel-measure" class="math">{{ section }}.1 Borel測度</h3>
<div class="math-book">
<i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark"></i> <a href="#miyajima"><cite lang="ja">宮島</cite></a> 定義7.53&ndash;定義7.55
</div>
<p>\(\varOmega\)を位相空間とする．\(\varOmega\)の開集合全体\(\mathcal{O}\)によって生成される\(\sigma\)-加法族\(\sigma(\mathcal{O})\)を\(\varOmega\)の<strong>Borel集合族</strong>という．開集合全体を明示せずに\(\mathcal{B}(\varOmega)\)とも書く．</p>
<p>測度空間\((\varOmega,\,\mathcal{B}(\varOmega))\)の測度\(\mu\)を<strong>Borel測度</strong>という．Borel測度\(\mu\)が任意の\(S \in \mathcal{B}(\varOmega)\)について</p>
<ol class="math narrow">
  <li class="capr">\(\mu(S) = \sup \{\mu(K) \mid K \subseteq S,\,K \text{ compact}\}\)</li>
  <li class="capr">\(\mu(S) = \inf \{\mu(O) \mid S \subseteq O,\,O \text{ open}\}\)</li>
</ol>
<p>を満たすとき，\(\mu\)は<strong>正則</strong>(regular)であるという．</p>
